[normal]must
[normal] rely on a back-up boiler, 
[normal]likely to be 
[normal]fos
[normal]sil fuel
[normal],
[normal] during colder periods. Second, 
[normal]as outlined above, the burning of biomass to generate electricity is significantly less efficient than to produce heat. 
